defaultd with two CCS projects in the UK including t
defaulthe coal-fired 
defaultWhite Rose Project in North Yorkshire
default. T
defaulthis decision represents a positive step forward for CCS development in the UK. It is important that the infrastructure supporting these demonstration projec
defaultts, for example the pipeline, is designed to have the capacity and functionality to allow the development of other projects as part of a cluster.  
defaultPolicy and financial support will also be needed in due course for CO
default2
default infrastructure based on other CCS clus
defaultters.
default4.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
